snippet.title: LUCID Demo Extended Sneak Peek
snippet.description:
WISHLIST LUCID ON STEAM - https://store.steampowered.com/app/1717730/LUCID/

Friends!  I’m excited to share some of the progress being made on the LUCID demo!
Can you spot what is new? Enemies? Stage Hazards? Environments?
Let me know what you see and I’ll happily expand on it in the comments!
Please consider sharing to your stories my friends, I’d greatly appreciate it.
Thank you all so much for your support. I couldn’t do this without you ❤

LUCID DISCORD ❤️ - https://discord.com/invite/PQYTsAZQZu

** song is from MMX3 and its purpose is to set the tone, original OST will be in final game **
